com.ikala.android.bdl.tracking.transaction

Class TransactionParam

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ikala.android.bdl.tracking.transaction.TransactionParam

  • public class TransactionParam
extends Object
    TransactionParam contains all the keys of Transaction parameters. You can use these constants as the Bundle key to generate a parameters Bundle for Tracker.addTransaction(TransactionName, Bundle).
    See Also:
    Tracker.addTransaction(TransactionName, Bundle)
